<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Fisica II — Dispense Interattive</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@300;400;600&display=swap');
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:'Source Sans 3',sans-serif;background:#faf9f6;color:#1a1a1e;min-height:100vh}
.topbar{background:#1a1a1e;padding:14px 32px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.topbar a{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);text-decoration:none;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;transition:color 0.15s}
.topbar a:hover{color:#fff}
.topbar span{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);font-size:12px}
.hero{background:#1a1a1e;color:#fff;padding:56px 32px 44px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 100%,rgba(181,53,26,0.18),transparent 70%)}
.eyebrow{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin-bottom:14px;font-weight:600}
.hero h1{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,46px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:10px}
.hero h1 em{color:#e07a5a;font-style:italic}
.hero p{font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);font-weight:300;max-width:420px;margin:0 auto}
.container{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:52px 32px}
@media(max-width:600px){.container{padding:36px 16px}.topbar{padding:12px 16px}}
.section-label{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#b5351a;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:22px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.section-label::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:#dddbd5}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:18px;margin-bottom:40px}
.card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #dddbd5;border-radius:6px;padding:26px 26px 60px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:block;transition:transform 0.18s,box-shadow 0.18s;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:3px;height:100%;transition:width 0.18s}
.card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)}
.card:hover::before{width:5px}
.card.blue::before{background:#1a4b8c}.card.blue:hover .card-arrow{color:#1a4b8c}
.card.red::before{background:#b5351a}.card.red:hover .card-arrow{color:#b5351a}
.card.purple::before{background:#5a1a8c}.card.purple:hover .card-arrow{color:#5a1a8c}
.card-num{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#bbb;margin-bottom:10px}
.card h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:19px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:#1a1a1e;line-height:1.25}
.card p{font-size:13px;color:#6b6860;line-height:1.6;font-weight:300}
.card-tags{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;position:absolute;bottom:18px;left:26px;right:44px}
.tag{font-size:10px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:2px;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600}
.tag-blue{background:#e8f0fa;color:#1a4b8c}
.tag-red{background:#fdf0ed;color:#b5351a}
.tag-purple{background:#f3eefa;color:#5a1a8c}
.tag-gray{background:#f0ede6;color:#6b6860}
.card-arrow{position:absolute;bottom:20px;right:22px;font-size:20px;color:#dddbd5;transition:color 0.18s,transform 0.18s}
.card:hover .card-arrow{transform:translateX(3px)}
footer{text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:#aaa;padding:28px;border-top:1px solid #dddbd5;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="topbar">
  <a href="../index.html">← Home</a>
  <span>/</span>
  <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600">Fisica II</span>
</div>
<div class="hero">
  <div class="eyebrow">Fisica II — Elettrostatica</div>
  <h1>Dispense di<br><em>Fisica</em></h1>
  <p>Campo elettrico, potenziale e distribuzioni di carica con simulatori interattivi</p>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="section-label">Elettrostatica</div>
  <div class="grid">

    <a class="card blue" href="../simulatore_campo_elettrico.html">
      <div class="card-num">Fisica 01</div>
      <h2>Il Campo Elettrico</h2>
      <p>Linee di campo di fino a 4 cariche puntiformi. Simulatore grafico con zoom e calcolatore numerico con unità reali (µC, nC, m, cm).</p>
      <div class="card-tags">
        <span class="tag tag-blue">Simulatore 2D</span>
        <span class="tag tag-blue">Calcolatore E</span>
      </div>
      <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card red" href="../dispensa_potenziale_completa.html">
      <div class="card-num">Fisica 02</div>
      <h2>Il Potenziale Elettrico</h2>
      <p>Equipotenziali 2D e superficie 3D di V(x,y) per fino a 4 cariche. Vista ruotabile.</p>
      <div class="card-tags">
        <span class="tag tag-red">2D + 3D</span>
        <span class="tag tag-gray">Equipotenziali</span>
      </div>
      <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
    </a>

    <a class="card purple" href="../dispensa_distribuzioni.html">
      <div class="card-num">Fisica 03</div>
      <h2>Distribuzioni di Carica</h2>
      <p>Campo di piano, retta, sfera e conduttore irregolare. Mappa |E| e effetto punta.</p>
      <div class="card-tags">
        <span class="tag tag-purple">4 simulatori</span>
        <span class="tag tag-gray">Effetto punta</span>
      </div>
      <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
    </a>

  </div>
</div>
<footer>Didattica Pierri · Fisica II · Elettrostatica</footer>
</body>
</html>

</html>
